Class WinEventsLogger

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILogger

    public class WinEventsLogger
extends AbstractLog4JLogger
    Logger which appends messages to the Windows Event Log. This only works on Windows and requires the file NTEventLogAppender.dll in a directory on the PATH (e.g. C:\Windows\system32).
